"title": "5454: power, God's saving",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5454: power, god's saving",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God has power to save and protect and through his power he will defeat those who oppose him.</p>\n<h2>God's power to save</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:6\">PSA 20:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:12\">2CH 20:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:15\">2CH 20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9-Isa40:10\">ISA 40:9–40:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3-2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:3–1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's power to perform miracles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:19\">LUK 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54\">MAT 13:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:2\">MAT 14:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:14\">MRK 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:30\">MRK 5:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:46\">LUK 8:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:36\">LUK 4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17\">LUK 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h2>God's power to protect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:26-Dan6:27\">DAN 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a></p>\n<h2>God's people pray for God to act in power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:11\">2CH 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:12\">2CH 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:1-Ps68:2\">PSA 68:1–68:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:28\">PSA 68:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:9\">JER 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:23-Acts4:31\">ACT 4:23–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a></p>\n<h2>The power of the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16\">ROM 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:21\">ROM 4:21</a> <em>God has power to fulfil his promises</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6\">ROM 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3\">ROM 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a></p>\n<h2>The power of God's kingdom</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:1\">MRK 9:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:19-1Cor4:20\">1CO 4:19–4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Preaching and power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:33\">ACT 4:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:22\">ACT 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:17-1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:17–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:7\">EPH 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7-2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:7–1:8</a></p>\n<h2>The powers that oppose God will be defeated</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24\">1CO 15:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">COL 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:21\">ISA 24:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:15-Isa59:20\">ISA 59:15–59:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:26-Dan7:27\">DAN 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:10\">REV 18:10</a></p>\n<h2>The power of God over death</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:48\">PSA 89:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:8\">ECC 8:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:8\">ISA 25:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:14\">HOS 13:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:26\">1CO 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:44\">1CO 15:42–15:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:54–15:57</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></p>",
